history.content: Secondary sections are taught by GSIs and each class has a budget which is used to pay for GSIs. Smaller classes have smaller budgets. This class is quite small and unfortunately only 1 DIS section can be offered. The class schedule has been set for quite some time and after enrollment occurs we cannot change the times.

Is there any way there can be another section time added for EE130? Right now there is only one section time and that makes it very inflexible to integrate the class into existing schedules..I understand the class size is relatively small but it feels a little inhibiting for there to only be one option for section time available. Thanks!
history.subject: EE130 additional section time?
